1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Here's what science actually says about alcohol sleep quality.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:08,400
Many think alcohol helps them sleep, but the reality is more complex.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:13,200
Research shows it can disrupt REM sleep, the phase crucial for restoration.

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:17,600
Studies indicate that even low amounts can reduce overall sleep quality.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:23,600
So, while a drink may help you fall asleep, you'll likely wake up feeling worse.

6
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,600
Want to improve your sleep?

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,600
Consider cutting back on alcohol.

8
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,600
Follow for more science insights!
